WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.200
Captain Nova stands in a futuristic launch bay facing a tall rocket while holographic controls and space light the room.

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:04.600
The bay brightens with blue and orange power as the launch path opens ahead of the rocket.

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:07.200
The rocket lifts off and races through a glowing corridor of stars and colored energy.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:10.042
The flight resolves into a wide alien landscape where Captain Nova arrives at a calm, radiant destination.
